# read in packages
```{r}
library(tidyverse)
library(naniar)
```


read in data
```{r}
cort = read_csv('../Data/Project0_Clean_v2.csv')
```


```{r}
head(cort)
```

check missingness
```{r}
vis_miss(cort)
```

look at missing outcome values
```{r}
cort %>% filter(is.na(`DHEA (pg/dl)`))
```
missing cortisol values are coded as 9999!


```{r}
cort %>% filter(`Cortisol (ug/dl)` == 9999)
```
